@DeanLand @jeffJarvis -- what @deanland is referring to (I assume) is Drummer, which is a product I developed last year and shipped in October that does blogging the way I initially imagined it would be done back in 1997. We took a wrong turn imho, and Drummer gets us back on track.

@DeanLand @jeffjarvis Drummer is different, it's not like Blogger or Movable Type or my own Radio UserLand, from the early 00s. All your blogging is done from a single document, an outline. Posts do not require titles (like Twitter).

